        "body": "This PR cleans up `editor/js/libs/tern-threejs/threejs.js` by removing properties that are no longer present in the core library geometry.\r\n\r\nAs identified in issue #30657, the following deprecated fields have been deleted:\r\n- `lineDistances`\r\n- `lineDistancesNeedUpdate`\r\n- `verticesNeedUpdate`\r\n- `normalNeedUpdate`\r\n\r\nThese fields were confirmed to be nonexistent in the current Three.js source code.\r\n\r\ndone and previewed by soham goel",
