        },
        "body": "User Model Updated\r\n\r\nAdded recentRooms array in User.js to store last 10 room codes with timestamps.\r\n\r\nJoin Room Controller\r\n\r\nCreated joinRoom() in roomController.js to update user's recentRooms.\r\n\r\nAPI Routes Added\r\n\r\nPOST /api/rooms/join to track joined room\r\n\r\nGET /api/users/me/recent-rooms to fetch recent rooms\r\n\r\nJWT Auth Middleware\r\n\r\nAdded auth.js to protect the above routes\r\n\r\nRegistered Routes in app.js\r\n\r\n\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Introduced user authentication with JWT for secure API access.\n  * Added functionality to join rooms and track recently joined rooms.\n  * Implemented API endpoints to join rooms and fetch a user's recent rooms.\n  * Added a responsive navigation bar with mobile menu support.\n  * Introduced a poll component allowing users to submit and view poll responses.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
